Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,expression of of its own design as an\Nexpression of its own potentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.00,0:03:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming an actuality.\NAnd it's so everything is unfolding of
