Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,all you can ever witness is potentiality\Nbecoming actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.23,0:04:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And because it's happening in form, you\Nthink there's separation.
