Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Newtonian paradigm, they would\Nyou could start setting it up, setting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it up like this is causing this, causing\Nthis, causing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing is causing anything because the\Nfield really lights a butterfly on this.
