Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it goes there. See, but there's nothing\Ncausing it to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,See, life then is an unfoldingness of\Npotentiality
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,becoming actuality.\NAnd you see that all things are just
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,happening spontaneously of their own.\NJust like this lady's son or whoever it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.60,0:05:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,is is going to bring himself right down\Nto frankly killing himself and maybe
